---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Keynotes — Nellie Borrero" description="Transformative keynote topics on inclusive leadership, championing the underrecognized, and sustaining inclusivity." path="/services">
	<section class="container py-12">
		<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-plum">Keynotes</h1>
		<p class="mt-3 max-w-prose text-lg">Bring Nellie to your audience</p>
		
		<!-- Main Keynote Topics -->
		<div class="mt-12 space-y-12">
			<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-8 bg-white">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plum mb-4">Championing the underrecognized</h2>
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">How leaders can make careers thrive</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">What does it mean to truly lead and advocate for underrepresented communities within organizations? In her book Unwavering, Nellie Borrero shows leaders how to help ensure equal opportunities for every employee and guide individuals from historically marginalized communities throughout their career journeys.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-8 bg-white">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plum mb-4">The Inclusion Momentum</h2>
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Sustaining inclusivity in the workplace DNA</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Leaders often struggle to sustain Inclusion progress when they face new challenges or disruptions. Nellie offers a roadmap for leaders based on her own experience building and nurturing a culture of belonging and empowerment through lasting initiatives.</p>
			</article>

			<article class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-8 bg-white">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-plum mb-4">Being unapologetically you</h2>
				<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Become an advocate for yourself</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Confidently stepping into your power and safeguarding your identity in the workplace can be challenging, especially for people from traditionally underrepresented populations. Through her personal story in Unwavering, Nellie flips the narrative and shows that what makes you different makes you powerful.</p>
			</article>
		</div>

		<!-- Categories and Audiences Grid -->
		<div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 bg-white">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-plum mb-4">Categories</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
					<li>• Leadership</li>
					<li>• Business management</li>
					<li>• Corporate culture</li>
					<li>• Change management</li>
					<li>• Talent management life cycle</li>
					<li>• Workforce dynamics: diversity, teamwork, motivation, equity and inclusiveness and more</li>
					<li>• Generational workforce dynamics</li>
					<li>• Aligning ERG strategy and leadership with business priorities</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 p-6 bg-white">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-plum mb-4">Audiences</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
					<li>• Corporations, non-profits and educational institutions</li>
					<li>• CEOs, C-suite executives</li>
					<li>• Board members</li>
					<li>• Executive teams</li>
					<li>• Human Resources executives</li>
					<li>• Diversity, Equity and Inclusion executives/thought leaders</li>
					<li>• People leaders and management teams</li>
					<li>• Professionals at any career level who crave a more inclusive, high trust, high-performing organization</li>
					<li>• Professionals at any career level who are looking to build, nurture, and evolve their personal brand and learn how to be unapologetically themselves</li>
					<li>• Students</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-12 text-center">
			<a class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4" href="mailto:contact@nellieborrero.com">Contact Nellie Borrero</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

